summary:
A small collection of Saved Games, all at Level 1 just ready to exit the Helgen Cave.
These are Racemenu generated Characters that can be saved as presets in Racemenu if you wish.
descriptionHtml:
Most races are included, All Female, sorry, and no beast races.

These should be pretty clean saves.  No quests finished, no scripts running.


I don't think these girls will come out well without this and it's requirements  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Racemenu

[/url]I use UNPB bodies with HDT. 
Textures are Women of Skyrim.
KS Hairdos Renewal

I can't take any credit for anything, I just made a selection of save games that avoid most of Helgen.

This is a save file from Legendary Edition, and so forever incompatible with SSE.
author: Teofa Tsavo
